1.title: Million Dollar Log Castles
1.plot: Kevin and Jennifer are escaping city life and are looking at three one-of-a-kind log mansions. $1.5 million offers homes with the best views and some unique features that only Northern Minnesotans will need!

2.title: Mountain Log Homes
2.plot: Matt and Genevieve are newlyweds looking to purchase their first home and they want a log cabin. They are looking at a cabin on the river, a cabin that takes an hour off-roading to find and a cabin that comes with 17 acres of privacy.

imdb.plot outline: When a family who wants to leave the hustle and bustle of the big city has a choice of three cabins with awesome features and a budget of $1.5 million, which will they choose? A newlywed couple hooked on fly fishing must decide if they want to be on the river, more remote, or have 17 private acres to themselves.
